The Nairobi Burger Festival is back again and it is bigger and juicier than ever! The festival started on May 8 and will end on is on May 14. This will be the second annual Burger Festival in Partnership with Visa and it's set to take place at over 90 restaurants around Nairobi and for the very first time, Mombasa.You know the drill, but just in case you need a reminder, there's only one step you need to take to participate in this year's #BurgerFest and that is to make sure you've downloaded your Burger Festival pass from this link.Then you're good to go! Show the pass at any of the participating restaurants and you'll get another burger free.Click here for a full list of participating restaurants.Happy Burger-ing! email print email print